result.name: 權記雲吞麵

reviews.text: Good value for having meal here, it is relatively cheap but good taste. The shrimps wonton is big in size. It is worth to have a taste in here.

A little hidden treasure in Wan Chai for authentic local style wonton noodle soup.

Other than wonton, they also have a lot of other toppings on offer, such as beef brisket, different types do dumplings, fresh beef, fish ball etc.

Not to mention, this is the place to come when your pocket feels a bit empty, most noodles are only HK$20, it’s a great piece!
Springy noodles, flavourful soup base, fresh wontons with generous whole shrimp filling, peppery pork balls, spicy chlili sauce on the side ... For HKD20 great value for money and super delicious!
相信是灣仔最便宜的雲吞麵，但一點也不馬虎，麵條爽口，道地的香港味道，讚👍
店家乾淨舒適，冷氣强，上菜速度快，服務員態度佳。
